data.description: You will not want to miss this fantastic home. This amazing home is located on a 1 acre heavily wooded lot.  The home itself has an awesome curb appeal. Covered front porch, entryway is wide and spacious. Living room has a tray ceiling, crown molding,  ceiling fan. stacked stone finish on fireplace with a metal insert, and a gorgeous mantle.  Kitchen has a large walk-in pantry, Kitchen island, granite counter tops, open concept to living room.  Dining area and living room have lots windows to overlook the wooded acre while enjoying morning coffee. Primary bedroom is quite large, ceiling fan, lots of windows, primary bath has awesome walk in shower. double vanity sink, and the primary closet is huge  and it opens up to the laundry room. Just past the laundry room is a beautiful built in mud bench with tons of storage, which is located right as you come in from the garage. The office has beautiful french doors, crown molding, and a ceiling fan. Spare bedrooms are separated by a guest bath. Both have ceiling fans.  Plus there is so much storage in this home.  What an amazing Home.  You will fall in love with it.
